name: Superb AI
headline: Superb AI is a training data management platform
description: Superb AI helps you effortlessly label, manage, and curate training datasets for computer vision and makes rapid, consistent iteration a reality.

founders.description:

- Duke University, B.S / Ph.D. dropout
